  "title": "Early Years Teacher| Preschool EY2",
  "description": "<ul><li>Design and execute lesson plans with age-appropriate materials </li><li>Foster positive behaviours in the preschool centre </li><li>Evalute lesson plans and admend accordingly to the needs of the children </li><li>Conduct obersvation and update parents on child's progression</li><li>Provide a safe and welcoming environment for the children</li><li>Adhere to HPB, ECDA and Centre SOP guidlines </li><li>Build strong parent-teacher partnership with two-ways communication and involvement</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Early Childhood Care & Education or relevant, with LON </li><li>Min 2 years related experience</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday </li></ul><p>Check out www.abercare.sg for more details</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may send in your resume to career@abercare.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
